metadata.description: Temporal scope steering via inherent activity time horizons. Uses conceptual understanding of natural time scales (brush teeth → minutes, graduate → years). Trained with category-based split for zero data leakage. Generalizes to unseen categories.
example_pairs: After I brush my teeth, I will: (A) Get into bed (B) Plan my retirement
After I graduate, I will: (A) Celebrate with friends (B) Start building my career
After I finish this sentence, I will: (A) Start the next one (B) Publish my collected works
